                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-500">
                                <User className="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-blue-500" />
                                {/* {church.leader} */}Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis urna nulla, ultricies eu eros ut, molestie ullamcorper quam. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia curae;
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-500">
                                <Calendar className="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-blue-500" />
                                {/* Founded: {church.founded} */}
                                Founded:Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis urna nulla, ultricies eu eros ut, molestie ullamcorper quam. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia curae;
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow border-t border-slate-100 pt-4">
                            {/* {church.description} */}
                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis urna nulla, ultricies eu eros ut, molestie ullamcorper quam. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia curae;
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="mt-auto">
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform cursor-pointer">
                                View Details <ArrowRight className="w-4 h-4 ml-1" />
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            ))}
        </div>

    </div>
</section>